<ab facs="#facs_501_r3l19">~ dem <expan>Römıſche<ex>n</ex></expan> etc Künıg / an <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> guten freẅnde ~ der freyen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_501_r3l20">vnd Reıchs Stette <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>botte<ex>n</ex></expan> dıe <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> bey vns <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ſınd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_501_r3l21"><expan>begeru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> beſchehen ıſt / vnd auch von <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>treffenlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> ſache </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_501_r3l22"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / Jſt vns von <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> ſtette <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>botte<ex>n</ex></expan> befolhen <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_501_r3l25"><expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> vnd 
<add><ab facs="#facs_501_r3l24">den </ab></add> <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſtett<ex>en</ex></expan> in <expan>franke<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_501_r3l23">guten </ab></add> <expan>freẅnd<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_501_r3l26">nachpawrn / <expan>ʒuv<ex>er</ex>ſchreıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> Jr <expan>erb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> in kürcʒ <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒu </ab>
