<pb facs="#facs_502"/>
<ab facs="#facs_502_r3l2">mıt fleıſſ vnd <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> an eẅr <expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> daʒ Jr eẅr <expan>erb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> </ab>
