<ab facs="#facs_502_line_1592199828964_1057">Lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>vıgı<ex>lia</ex></expan> . <expan>Natı<ex>ui</ex>tat<ex>is</ex></expan> marıe <expan>virg<ex>in</ex>ıs</expan> </ab>
