</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_501"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Weissemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>, Winsheim, Rotemburg und Sweinfurt yeder
                        stat</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, von sache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> dem <expan>römische<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                        künig an <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> guten frewnde der freyen und reichs
                        stette <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>botte<ex>n</ex></expan>, die <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> bey
                        uns <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> sind, <expan>begeru<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
                        beschehen ist und auch von <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>treffenlich<ex>er</ex></expan> sache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                        ist uns von <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan> stette
                            <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>botte<ex>n</ex></expan> befolhen <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> und <add>den</add>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>stett<ex>en</ex></expan> in <expan>Franke<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<add>guten</add>
<expan>frewnd<ex>en</ex></expan> und nachpawrn, <expan>zu
                                v<ex>er</ex>schreibe<ex>n</ex></expan>, ir
                            <expan>erb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> in kürcz <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu
                        uns zu <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>, sie
                            <expan>söllich<ex>er</ex></expan> sachen müntlich zu
                                <expan>unt<ex>er</ex>richten</expan> und uns <add>auch</add>
<expan>miteinand<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> zu <expan>unt<ex>er</ex>reden</expan>. Also
                                <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir <pb facs="#facs_502"/>mit fleiss
                        und <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> an ewr
                            <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>, daz ir ewr
                            <expan>erb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> rate auf
                        den nehsten sunntag zu nacht zu uns <add>gen
                                <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan></add> also
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> schiket und des niht lasset. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>vigi<ex>lia</ex></expan>
<expan>nati<ex>vi</ex>tat<ex>is</ex></expan> Marie
                            <expan>virg<ex>in</ex>is</expan>.</ab>
</div>
